query:
SELECT c.id, c.name, c.email 
FROM customers c 
JOIN orders o ON c.id = o.customer_id 
WHERE o.amount > 1000 
  AND o.order_date >= date_trunc('month', CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 month') 
  AND o.order_date < date_trunc('month', CURRENT_DATE) 
GROUP BY c.id, c.name, c.email;
